description: Amundi Euro Government Bond – UCITS ETF Acc seeks to replicate as closely as possible, whether the trend is rising of falling, the performance of the Bloomberg Euro Treasury 50bn Bond Index (the "Index"), while minimizing the tracking error between the performance of the Sub-Fund and the one of the Index. For further information on index rules, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
name: Amundi Euro Government Bond UCITS ETF Acc
